  "3283310": {
    "name": "Kioku: 夏日记忆岛",
    "steam_appid": 3283310,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/9e092749b89612e3701b8f2a2e098866.poster.avif?t=1771945530\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/9e092749b89612e3701b8f2a2e098866.webm?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/9e092749b89612e3701b8f2a2e098866.mp4?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏝️ 欢迎来到记忆岛，这是阿斯蒂的新家！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >骑上你的自行车随意闲逛，让每一天按自己的节奏慢慢展开。岛上到处都藏着小秘密，而最美好的瞬间往往发生在你放松的时候。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/536b5834f4cbd2110513dac738cbcaf0.poster.avif?t=1771945530\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/536b5834f4cbd2110513dac738cbcaf0.webm?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/536b5834f4cbd2110513dac738cbcaf0.mp4?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🦀 在温暖的夏日里捕捉螃蟹！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捕捉各种螃蟹，把它们加入你的收藏。每一次收获都像是小小的胜利，尤其是当稀有的惊喜突然出现时。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/2172b524581f5dccd3c69e3d834be5b2.poster.avif?t=1771945530\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/2172b524581f5dccd3c69e3d834be5b2.webm?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/2172b524581f5dccd3c69e3d834be5b2.mp4?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎴 《弹珠怪物》正成为岛上的新潮流！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打开卡包，解锁全新的弹珠怪物，组建一支你喜欢的队伍。向岛上的居民发起挑战，看着你的弹珠怪物啪嗒一声冲进竞技场，爽感十足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/509ca56ceb79be5bcb273ed93b6367e5.poster.avif?t=1771945530\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/509ca56ceb79be5bcb273ed93b6367e5.webm?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/509ca56ceb79be5bcb273ed93b6367e5.mp4?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👨‍👩‍👦 结识记忆岛的居民！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解岛上的居民，帮助他们，并慢慢融入这个社区。你结识的人越多，岛屿就越向你敞开——新的故事、新的地点，还有属于你的日常小片段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/fa62de73af8ada3ebf09e02ec6c9dc51.poster.avif?t=1771945530\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/fa62de73af8ada3ebf09e02ec6c9dc51.webm?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/fa62de73af8ada3ebf09e02ec6c9dc51.mp4?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🚲 在记忆岛上自由漫步！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记忆岛是一座适合漫步的温馨小岛，每一条小路、每一个角落都隐藏着秘密。从小镇街道和码头，一路走到森林小径、山间高地，还有那些带着一点神秘气息的地方。只要跟随你的好奇心，总能发现新的惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/72b25fb4f21609a6818bd8a7790a9c70.poster.avif?t=1771945530\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/72b25fb4f21609a6818bd8a7790a9c70.webm?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/72b25fb4f21609a6818bd8a7790a9c70.mp4?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏝️ <strong>探索：</strong>扮演阿斯蒂，自由探索这座充满秘密、捷径和意外惊喜的温馨开放式岛屿</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦀 <strong>小游戏：</strong>捕捉螃蟹、进行《弹珠怪物》对战，重温2000年代童年暑假的感觉</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 <strong>居民：</strong>结识令人难忘的岛上居民，建立友情，书写属于你的夏日故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📸 <strong>回忆：</strong>用游戏内的相机记录瞬间，通过照片重温你的冒险旅程</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛩️<strong>日式北欧风：</strong>探索融合日式与斯堪的纳维亚风格的独特世界</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/e0a259a994e2e2faf1614853fd777242.poster.avif?t=1771945530\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/e0a259a994e2e2faf1614853fd777242.webm?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283310/extras/e0a259a994e2e2faf1614853fd777242.mp4?t=1771945530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☀️<i> 欢迎将游戏加入愿望单，并体验试玩版！感谢你游玩我们的第一款游戏 c: ——Lugn Games</i></strong></h2>",
